[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has both Majors and enough points to open 2\C. 
NORTH, with 4 points, responds with a negative 2\D.

SOUTH first bids her higher ranking suit, 2\S. 
NORTH is too strong for second negative, he bids 2NT.

SOUTH now shows her second suit, 3\H.

NORTH is happy to bid the game in \Hs.}

